{"tid":1367109,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"航空業界機場集會　向旅客發「警告」：不要相信香港警方和政府","createTime":"2019-07-26T07:07:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T07:07:29.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1eef01aab71732292d03698617f6c740c8d32c5a","tid":1367109,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:07:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/67374494_10161874707135265_2220261959025033216_o20copy_c2lZT_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F67374494_10161874707135265_2220261959025033216_o20copy_c2lZT_1200x0.png&h=62160a73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府強推《逃犯條例》修訂引發社會矛盾，7.21 上環開槍和元朗襲擊後，更激起民憤，大批航空界職員包括空中服務員、機場地勤等，今日發起在機場接機大堂「接機」，要求政府起訴施襲者，成立獨立調查委員會徹查警暴，並向旅客介紹香港的情況，呼籲國際社會關注。<br />\n<br />\n集會在機場一號客運大樓接機大堂舉行，集會人士準備了不同語文的單張派發予旅客，包括印有「旅客警告」的標語，指警方在上環向和平示威者開槍，同時政府在新界僱用黑幫毆打示威者，「不要相信警方或政府」；他們又在現場播放元朗襲擊等新聞片段。除了航空業員工外，亦有市民響應號召到機場參與。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%8F%BE%E5%A0%B4%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD-%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E6%A5%AD%E7%95%8C%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83-%E5%90%91%E6%97%85%E5%AE%A2%E7%99%BC-%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A-%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E7%9B%B8%E4%BF%A1%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%92%8C%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%258F%25BE%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E7%259B%25B4%25E6%2592%25AD-%25E8%2588%25AA%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E7%2595%258C%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%259C%2583-%25E5%2590%2591%25E6%2597%2585%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E7%2599%25BC-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2591%258A-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25A6%2581%25E7%259B%25B8%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%2592%258C%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%2F&d=d2KrXihf468bG0awDawljqS5T01Y9%2BWuDWMC0%2BQyx7Y%3D&h=3b9708aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F